      "rationale": "No independent peer review of the simulation setup was documented. The hemolysis model constants (C, alpha, beta in the power-law model) were not verified against published sources by an independent reviewer. Flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
