      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but only two of the seven uncertain input parameters (pump speed tolerance and inlet flow rate) were included in the uncertainty propagation. Hemolysis model constants and viscosity model parameters were treated as deterministic. Achieved level 2 but flagged as incomplete assessment."
