    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a complete record of identified gaps. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six factors were identified as epistemic gaps and flagged as not-assessed. No factor met its required credibility level. The package documents the full gap profile as required by ASME V&V 40-2018 Section 6 for a not-accepted model use decision. The package is accepted as a complete evidence record despite the model use decision being Not Accepted.",
